Important notes

If strict preprocess fails at infiltration, landcover_2021.tif is missing/wrong format.
If strict preprocess fails at drains, ms4_outfalls.zip is likely GDB format; use shapefile zip or convert first.
For demos, keep both uvicorn and frontend dev server running.
